
REPORT ZVK_1.

*Data x Type i. "Variable declaration
*Data y Type i.
*Data z Type i.

 data : x type i, y type i, z type i.

*x=100. "Syntaxerror

 x = 10. "Initialization
 y = 20.
 z = x + y. "Addition
 write z.   "Display result
 write : / 'Addition of two numbers is', z.

 write : / 'Addition of two numbers is', z Left-Justified. " Here Left justified is an Option
 write : / 'Addition of two numbers is', z Centered.